message: "If you use Glassbox in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Glassbox 2.9: Mechanistic Interpretability, EU AI Act Compliance, Tamper-Evident Audit Log, TypeScript SDK, and Jupyter Widgets"
version: 2.9.0
date-released: "2026-03-20"
license: MIT
